NAME
    Foo - merge .pod files into their .pm counterparts

VERSION
    version 0.2.1

SYNOPSIS
        # in dist.ini
        [CoalescePod]

DESCRIPTION
    If the files *Foo.pm* and *Foo.pod* both exist, the content of the pod
    file is appended at the end of the ".pm", and the pod file is removed.

AUTHOR
    Yanick Champoux <yanick@babyl.dyndns.org>

